	font-size:13.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Noto Sans SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);
	letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;
	font-size:13.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="Noto Sans SC" >尽管当地法律和习俗对儿童的定义不同，但我们将不满</font><font face="Noto Sans SC" >14周岁的任何人均视为儿童。</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Noto Sans SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);
	letter-spacing:0.0000pt;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;
	font-size:13.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'Noto Sans SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);
